data.description: Looking for space, entertainment, and location? Well here you have 129 Corral, where you can call home with nothing short of everything you're looking for. This 2,423 sq ft home boast 4 bedrooms with a possibility of a 5th and 2.5 bathrooms. Upgrades are throughout and ready for turn key. You have an office space, dining room, and a kitchen that is open to the living room which floods with natural lightning! As if the home space alone isn't worth running for, run to the backyard where there's nothing but opportunity for entertainment. It keeps getting better, as this property is in WALKING distance to the Elementary, Junior High, High School, your neighborhood parks and the neighborhood swimming pool. It just does not get any better than this. Call today to schedule your tour!
